:: Extra Macros
{set _switchVal = "warrior"}
### Extra Macros

**Include macro:**

{include "Includable Passage"}

**Switch/case/default:**

{switch _switchVal}
  {case "mage"}
    You are a mage.
  {case "warrior"}
    You are a warrior.
  {default}
    Unknown class.
{/switch}

**Meter macro:**

{#hp-meter.health-bar meter $player.hp $player.maxHp "%"}

**Link macro:**

{link "Set flag" "Start"}
  {set $has_key = true}
{/link}

**Unset macro:**

{set $unset_test = "exists"}
Before unset: {$unset_test}.
{unset $unset_test}

**Story title:** {story-title}

**Passage tracking:**

{if hasVisited("Hallway")}
  You have visited the Hallway.
{else}
  You have NOT visited the Hallway.
{/if}

Visit count for Start: {print visited("Start")}

**Current passage:** {print currentPassage().name}

**Timed macro:**

{#timed-output timed 100ms}
  Timed content appeared!
  {next 100ms}
    Second section!
{/timed}

**Type macro:**

{#type-output type 10ms}Typed text here{/type}

**Repeat macro:**

{set $repeat_count = 0}
{#repeat-output repeat 50ms}
  {set $repeat_count = $repeat_count + 1}
  Tick {$repeat_count}.
  {if $repeat_count >= 3}{stop}{/if}
{/repeat}

**ID syntax on variable:** {#player-name-display $player.name}

**ID syntax on link:** [[#id-test-link Back to start|Start]]

[[Back to start|Start]]

