:: Interpolation Demo
{set $theme = "dark"}
{set _highlight = "active"}
### Interpolation Demo

**Dynamic class via selector interpolation:**

{.{$theme} print "themed content"}

{.prefix-{$theme} print "prefixed content"}

**Dynamic class via HTML attribute interpolation:**

<span class="{$theme}-text">HTML interpolated class</span>

<div class="box {$theme}" id="themed-box">Interpolated in attributes</div>

**Temporary variable interpolation:**

{.{_highlight} print "highlighted"}

**For loop with interpolated class:**

{for @item of ["alpha", "beta"]}
  <span class="item-{@item}">{@item}</span>
{/for}

