:: Edge Cases
{set _spaced = "hello world"}
{set _special = "test&value"}
{set _empty = ""}
{set _numstr = "42"}
{set _zero = 0}
{set _null_like = "null"}
{set _bool_false = false}
{set _bool_true = true}
{set _with_quotes = "it's a \"test\""}
### Edge Cases

**String with spaces:** {_spaced}

**String with ampersand:** {_special}

**Empty string display:** [{_empty}]

**Numeric string:** {_numstr}

**Zero value:** {_zero}

**Boolean false:** {_bool_false}

**Boolean true:** {_bool_true}

**Null-like string:** {_null_like}

**Conditional on empty string:**
{if _empty}empty is truthy{else}empty is falsy{/if}

**Conditional on zero:**
{if _zero}zero is truthy{else}zero is falsy{/if}

**Conditional on false:**
{if _bool_false}false is truthy{else}false is falsy{/if}

**Conditional on non-empty string:**
{if _spaced}spaced is truthy{else}spaced is falsy{/if}

**Print with arithmetic on numeric string:**
{print _numstr * 2}

**Comparison operators:**
{if $player.hp >= 100}hp-gte-100{/if}
{if $player.hp <= 100}hp-lte-100{/if}
{if $player.hp == 100}hp-eq-100{/if}
{if $player.hp !== 50}hp-neq-50{/if}

**Nested property access:**
{$player.name} has {$player.hp} HP

**Deep dot path on object:**
{print $player.healthStatus}

**For loop with index:**
{for @val, @idx of ["x", "y", "z"]}
  <span class="idx-item" id="idx-{@idx}">{@idx}:{@val}</span>
{/for}

**For loop over empty array:**
{for @item of []}SHOULD-NOT-APPEAR{/for}

**Nested if inside for:**
{for @n of [1, 2, 3]}
  {if @n == 2}<span class="found-two">two</span>{/if}
{/for}

**Multiple elseif chain:**
{set _chain = "c"}
{if _chain == "a"}chain-a{elseif _chain == "b"}chain-b{elseif _chain == "c"}chain-c{elseif _chain == "d"}chain-d{else}chain-default{/if}

**String concatenation in print:**
{print "Hello" + " " + "World"}

**Math expressions:**
{print Math.floor(7.9)}
{print Math.max(3, 7, 1)}
{print Math.min(10, 5, 20)}

[[Back to start|Start]]


