**At sign in value:** {$with_at}

**Underscore in value:** {$with_underscore}

**Multi-word value:** {$multi_word}

**Variable in bold markdown:** **{$player.name}**

**Variable in italic markdown:** *{$player.name}*

**Multiple variables in one line:** {$player.name} / {$player.hp} / {$player.strength}

**Literal curly braces:** This {is} not a macro

