:: For Loop Edge Cases
### For Loop Edge Cases

**Single item array:**
{for @item of ["only"]}
  <span class="single-item">{@item}</span>
{/for}

**Array with numbers:**
{for @num of [10, 20, 30]}
  <span class="num-item">{@num}</span>
{/for}

**Array with mixed types:**
{for @val of ["str", 42, true, false]}
  <span class="mixed-item">{@val}</span>
{/for}

**Nested for loops:**
{for @outer of ["A", "B"]}
  {for @inner of [1, 2]}
    <span class="nested-item">{@outer}-{@inner}</span>
  {/for}
{/for}

**For loop with button inside:**
{set $forBtnCount = 0}
{for @label of ["X", "Y"]}
  {button $forBtnCount = $forBtnCount + 1}{@label}{/button}
{/for}
For-btn count: {$forBtnCount}

**For loop with if inside:**
{for @n of [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]}
  {if @n % 2 == 0}<span class="even-num">{@n}</span>{/if}
{/for}

**For loop accessing story variable:**
{for @i of [0, 1]}
  <span class="inv-in-for">{print $inventory[@i]}</span>
{/for}

[[Back to start|Start]]


