:: Computed Var Tests
### Computed Variable Tests

{set _base = 10}
{computed _result = _base * 5}

**Basic computed:** {_result}

{set _base = 20}
**Computed after base change:** {_result}

{computed _fromStory = $player.hp + $player.strength}
**Computed from story vars:** {_fromStory}

{computed _conditional = $player.hp >= 100 ? "max" : "damaged"}
**Computed with ternary:** {_conditional}

{computed _stringComp = $player.name + " (Level " + $player.level + ")"}
