:: Unset Tests
### Unset Tests

{set $unset_a = "exists-a"}
{set $unset_b = "exists-b"}
{set _unset_temp = "exists-temp"}

**Before unset:**
A: {$unset_a}
B: {$unset_b}
Temp: {_unset_temp}

{unset $unset_a}
{unset _unset_temp}

**After unset:**
A: [{$unset_a}]
B: {$unset_b}
Temp: [{_unset_temp}]

